## React 19

| Requirement                                  | Details                                                                          |
| -------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **No `forwardRef`**                          | Deprecated in React 19; pass `ref` as a regular prop                             |

```tsx
// Bad
const DsButton = forwardRef<HTMLButtonElement, DsButtonProps>((props, ref) => {
  return <button ref={ref} {...props} />;
});

// Good
const DsButton = ({ ref, ...props }: DsButtonProps) => {
  return <button ref={ref} {...props} />;
};
```

